1115
01:41:35,301 --> 01:41:37,605
Boleh kita?

1116
01:41:48,545 --> 01:41:50,463
Fudge.

1117
01:41:52,025 --> 01:41:53,624
Mari, Hagrid.

1118
01:41:55,208 --> 01:41:56,797
Jadi?

1119
01:41:57,878 --> 01:41:59,106
